	body
		header.container-fluid.introduction
			a(href='#popup' id='openPopup' data-rel='popup' data-transition='pop')
				.col-md-1.login.login
					h3 Login 
			script.
				$('#openPopup').click(function(){
					$('#popup').show("slow", function(){
						$('#header').css("-animation-name: down; animation-time: 15s;");
						$('#popup').css("-animation-name: over;");
						});
					});
				$('#close').click(function(){
					$('#popup').hide("slow", function(){
						$('#header').css("animation-name: '';");
						});
					});
			.logo-beavent
			.col-md-8
				h3.subtitle Beavent connect people with events near them and shows the information about the place where its going on, the activities as its schedule and all of this, using beacons tecnology by Qualcomm. We used beacons because with them we can send notifications to any smartphone in a radio of approximate 50m and because its quite cheap to buy beacons. 
			a(href='#down')
